      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CALL ME FROSTY (4) comes here on the fresh side and has been moved to the Peter Fernie barn since his latest effort. He's jumped $1.65 two back and $3.70 last start in stronger maiden's than this. Looks well placed back to this level and can put his best foot forward. MAD SPITFIRE (3) is knocking on the door of a maiden win, missing by 2L when tiring from the front over 1400m last time out. Back to 1100m is the query, but he has early speed and he's right in this on his recent form. RULE THE REALM (1) missed narrowly two back before a 3.6L defeat at Geraldton last time out. Tsang's claim comes in handy his run two back at Albany rates highly for this. Can make an impression. WHERE'S THE HORSE (5) comes here off a long break but has shown glimpses at the trials. Keep safe. VERVAIN (2) is next best.",
